name: io.bytes.per.checksum
description:
The number of bytes per checksum.  Must not be larger than
  io.file.buffer.size.

name: mapreduce.jobhistory.move.thread-count
description: The number of threads used to move files.

name: dfs.qjournal.select-input-streams.timeout.ms
description: Timeout in milliseconds for accepting streams from JournalManagers.

name: ha.health-monitor.rpc-timeout.ms
description: Timeout for the actual monitorHealth() calls.

name: mapreduce.client.submit.file.replication
description:
The replication level for submitted job files.  This
  should be around the square root of the number of nodes.
